# GAFUS Project Rules

## Project Overview
This is a **fitness training management system** built with:
- **Next.js 15** (App Router)
- **TypeScript 5.8+**
- **Prisma** (PostgreSQL)
- **Material-UI**
- **BullMQ** (Background jobs)
- **Turborepo** (Monorepo)

## Language
- **All code comments, documentation, and user-facing text in Russian**
- Variable/function names in English
- Git commits in Russian

## Quick Reference
- **TypeScript:** Discriminated Unions, avoid `any` — `typescript.mdc`
- **Next.js:** Server Components by default, Server Actions — `nextjs.mdc`
- **Prisma:** `@gafus/prisma`, select only needed fields — `database.mdc`
- **React:** Functional components, hooks at top level — `react.mdc`
- **Errors:** try-catch, `@gafus/logger`, return `{ success, error }` — `error-handling.mdc`
- **Security:** auth, Zod, CSRF — `security.mdc`
- **Performance:** cache, optimize — `performance.mdc`
- **Documentation:** обновлять при изменениях — `documentation.mdc`

## File Organization
See **architecture.mdc** for monorepo and app structure. App: `app/`, `features/[feature]/{components,lib,types}`, `shared/`.

## Common Patterns
- **Server Action:** см. `nextjs.mdc`, `security.mdc`, `error-handling.mdc`
- **Discriminated Union:** см. `typescript.mdc`
